# 📊 Telecom Churn Analysis – Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

This project performs Exploratory Data Analysis on a sample telecom customer dataset to understand key drivers behind customer churn.

---

## 🔍 Objective

The goal is to analyze telecom customer behavior, identify patterns that contribute to churn, and uncover potential areas for business intervention using visual and statistical insights.

---

## 📁 Dataset

- `WA_Fn-UseC_-Telco-Customer-Churn.csv`  
  Contains features like customer ID, tenure, monthly charges, total charges, churn flag, and demographic attributes.

---

## 📊 Key Analysis Performed

- Summary statistics and data quality overview
- Churn distribution by customer type
- Visual correlations between Tenure & Monthly Charges
- Visualizing the charges via a correlation heatmap
`  
  Contains features like customer ID, tenure, monthly charges, total charges, churn flag, and demographic attributes.

